<br />\n<br />\n因為香港好似冇得讀，窮撚就要先讀 Psycho，賺夠再去外國讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715385758a67575b0b03de501ce98e2e3e9cc581","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2295c02cd0d4a8d7a738e7c1c5949939d6c40d96","tid":705593,"uid":121087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63cf5691726d7117e0b6ab771f4e065a5bb33509","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"非psy degree 要讀 1年psy course hku cu 都有 咁就當你有psy degree<br />\n<br />\n之後再報master cp psy 都係得cu 同hku 有<br />\n<br />\n我諗要background 好好先可以入到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"但1年psy course難唔難入？ 我淨係知cp個master難到痴線 但一年course就無乜人講"},{"pid":"1c98e14761578752b2fbf44f96a1960ff90386bd","tid":705593,"uid":121087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"715385758a67575b0b03de501ce98e2e3e9cc581","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2295c02cd0d4a8d7a738e7c1c5949939d6c40d96","tid":705593,"uid":121087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63cf5691726d7117e0b6ab771f4e065a5bb33509","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"非psy degree 要讀 1年psy course hku cu 都有 咁就當你有psy degree<br />\n<br />\n之後再報master cp psy 都係得cu 同hku 有<br />\n<br />\n我諗要background 好好先可以入到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"但1年psy course難唔難入？ 我淨係知cp個master難到痴線 但一年course就無乜人講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T15:27:07.000Z","msg":"你有degree 就入到 大學用黎cap水 <br />\n<br />\n好似十幾萬一年"},{"pid":"fd4ed8569fd88c7f55d527466064aa72f87cb8f7","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"係咪應該要係讀paycho master 個陣瘋狂r ra個啲做？定係做intern好啲？"},{"pid":"812432d8e5d07e0c27df02131d8251c556122298","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77aac5cd0b7cccb6c03ca2852b18971dce6c0fa9","tid":705593,"uid":83500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4ed8569fd88c7f55d527466064aa72f87cb8f7","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"係咪應該要係讀paycho master 個陣瘋狂r ra個啲做？定係做intern好啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T15:37:37.000Z","msg":"其實冇都冇問題 報CP過到screening係主要睇你character同maturity"},{"pid":"67ef71ddc0bfa739331d8b407ff039904e0a95a5","tid":705593,"uid":182401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e8ed835016216aac8f5338551eac6b68063d2e6c","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"對入呢行好大興趣，但知道係超難入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以好想入到嘅人分享下係點做到<br />\n<br />\n宜家係三大讀緊非psy degree, 上網睇過係要用master/ pgd in psy 轉入去 master in cp. 所以想問下hku cu master of psychology 易唔易入？ <br />\n<br />\n同埋佢地寫住prefer one year working experience (even not related to psy), 想fg就讀master in psy係咪冇機？ <br />\n<br />\n希望有成功入到嘅人指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 現職cp 識答盡答<br />\n<br />\n1.) MA / MPsy 應該唔太難入。我冇讀過，所以只係估計。<br />\n<br />\n2.）想讀cp 必須成績好，同埋性格適合，溝通表達能力好。就算你GPA 爆四，都要後者配合。<br />\n<br />\n3.）MA 入面我相信競爭亦好大，因為個個都想搏上去。又要付出一年全職讀書，當然大競爭。<br />\n<br />\n4.）兩大都會收返少數自己MA 人。個人建議讀兩大比較好。其他本地大學就...唔洗考慮。<br />\n<br />\n5.）最後提一句：CP program 僧多粥少到爆，兩大一年收約四十人。本地加外地Psy grad 人數，再加埋MA MPsy 畢業生。成功率可想而知。所以我嘅建議係：唔好期望太高，盡力試下無妨。為興趣讀psy, 會好過一啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9850d3fd76edd2fd36f72e5afe30b458ef7afe5","tid":705593,"uid":182401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2341cecdf9ca89a2c348d4632a85aabe6c6788","tid":705593,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:32:31.000Z","msg":"前題要先有舊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為香港好似冇得讀，窮撚就要先讀 Psycho，賺夠再去外國讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"唔係。唔洗去外國。香港HKU 同CU 有得讀。<br />\n兩年 full time UGC funded program"},{"pid":"91379f7b6533a08e03f28bcb949f2fc3b6050ef9","tid":705593,"uid":41849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人係澳洲cp master 返黎既？"},{"pid":"f5cb901a0f8420e03da6440be64dc8719650aed4","tid":705593,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9850d3fd76edd2fd36f72e5afe30b458ef7afe5","tid":705593,"uid":182401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2341cecdf9ca89a2c348d4632a85aabe6c6788","tid":705593,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:32:31.000Z","msg":"前題要先有舊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為香港好似冇得讀，窮撚就要先讀 Psycho，賺夠再去外國讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"唔係。唔洗去外國。香港HKU 同CU 有得讀。<br />\n兩年 full time UGC funded program"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"難入到仆街呀<br />\n去外國應該會易入d"},{"pid":"c026e211f264efff7bc70f64a2e513c85c22b1c2","tid":705593,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91379f7b6533a08e03f28bcb949f2fc3b6050ef9","tid":705593,"uid":41849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人係澳洲cp master 返黎既？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:59:57.000Z","msg":"or 其他國家都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d71723467a2569b6acec616f4bca46e30d9300","tid":705593,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/120531_85185c0c6e2ede9e20a09105ac461b34.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F120531_85185c0c6e2ede9e20a09105ac461b34.gif&h=2612a943&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48d701353593770f4491690898a83377f99af4cd","tid":705593,"uid":182401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91379f7b6533a08e03f28bcb949f2fc3b6050ef9","tid":705593,"uid":41849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人係澳洲cp master 返黎既？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:15:44.000Z","msg":"你指澳洲返嚟執業？<br />\n有啊"},{"pid":"adc4a20abac0b1281cd87359dfba4f1aba265c75","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67ef71ddc0bfa739331d8b407ff039904e0a95a5","tid":705593,"uid":182401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e8ed835016216aac8f5338551eac6b68063d2e6c","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"對入呢行好大興趣，但知道係超難入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以好想入到嘅人分享下係點做到<br />\n<br />\n宜家係三大讀緊非psy degree, 上網睇過係要用master/ pgd in psy 轉入去 master in cp. 所以想問下hku cu master of psychology 易唔易入？ <br />\n<br />\n同埋佢地寫住prefer one year working experience (even not related to psy), 想fg就讀master in psy係咪冇機？ <br />\n<br />\n希望有成功入到嘅人指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 現職cp 識答盡答<br />\n<br />\n1.) MA / MPsy 應該唔太難入。我冇讀過，所以只係估計。<br />\n<br />\n2.）想讀cp 必須成績好，同埋性格適合，溝通表達能力好。就算你GPA 爆四，都要後者配合。<br />\n<br />\n3.）MA 入面我相信競爭亦好大，因為個個都想搏上去。又要付出一年全職讀書，當然大競爭。<br />\n<br />\n4.）兩大都會收返少數自己MA 人。個人建議讀兩大比較好。其他本地大學就...唔洗考慮。<br />\n<br />\n5.）最後提一句：CP program 僧多粥少到爆，兩大一年收約四十人。本地加外地Psy grad 人數，再加埋MA MPsy 畢業生。成功率可想而知。所以我嘅建議係：唔好期望太高，盡力試下無妨。為興趣讀psy, 會好過一啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T13:55:59.000Z","msg":"Thanks 巴打咁詳細咁答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，巴打係咪first hon入？"},{"pid":"ebf44efda02e040c84fcac3ef46717c2ed991952","tid":705593,"uid":182401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adc4a20abac0b1281cd87359dfba4f1aba265c75","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67ef71ddc0bfa739331d8b407ff039904e0a95a5","tid":705593,"uid":182401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e8ed835016216aac8f5338551eac6b68063d2e6c","tid":705593,"uid":127895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"對入呢行好大興趣，但知道係超難入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以好想入到嘅人分享下係點做到<br />\n<br />\n宜家係三大讀緊非psy degree, 上網睇過係要用master/ pgd in psy 轉入去 master in cp. 所以想問下hku cu master of psychology 易唔易入？ <br />\n<br />\n同埋佢地寫住prefer one year working experience (even not related to psy), 想fg就讀master in psy係咪冇機？ <br />\n<br />\n希望有成功入到嘅人指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 現職cp 識答盡答<br />\n<br />\n1.) MA / MPsy 應該唔太難入。我冇讀過，所以只係估計。<br />\n<br />\n2.）想讀cp 必須成績好，同埋性格適合，溝通表達能力好。就算你GPA 爆四，都要後者配合。<br />\n<br />\n3.）MA 入面我相信競爭亦好大，因為個個都想搏上去。又要付出一年全職讀書，當然大競爭。<br />\n<br />\n4.）兩大都會收返少數自己MA 人。個人建議讀兩大比較好。其他本地大學就...唔洗考慮。<br />\n<br />\n5.）最後提一句：CP program 僧多粥少到爆，兩大一年收約四十人。本地加外地Psy grad 人數，再加埋MA MPsy 畢業生。成功率可想而知。所以我嘅建議係：唔好期望太高，盡力試下無妨。為興趣讀psy, 會好過一啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c